==English==
===Etymology===
From [[console]] + [[-able]]. Derived from French [[consoler]], from Latin [[consolari]], which is from [[con-]] + [[solari]] (to soothe).

===Adjective===
'''consolable'''
#Able or likely to be [[console]]d.

